OL,3,C'Kind and talented': Tributes paid to
OL,4,CLiam Payne after his death
OL,6,FPeople in Wolverhampton, where Liam
OL,7,Fspent his childhood, have been
OL,8,Fremembering the singer, as Hannah
OL,9,FLudlow reports.
OL,11,FTributes have been made to
OL,12,FWolverhampton-born Liam Payne after
OL,13,Fthe One Direction star died aged 31.
OL,15,FHis family have said they are
OL,16,F"heartbroken", adding: "Liam will
OL,17,Fforever live in our hearts and we'll
OL,18,Fremember him for his kind, funny and
OL,19,Fbrave soul."
