OL,3,C'Kind and talented': Tributes paid to
OL,4,CLiam Payne after his death
OL,6,FIt comes after Payne fell from a third
OL,7,Ffloor balcony of a hotel in Argentina,
OL,8,Faccording to local police.
OL,10,FHe grew up and went to school and
OL,11,Fcollege in Wolverhampton, where many
OL,12,Fof his friends and family still live.
OL,14,F"I'll remember Liam as being that
OL,15,Flovely lad from Wolverhampton"
OL,17,FLiam Payne's school friend, James
OL,18,FPotts said: "It's a real shame what
OL,19,Fhappened, he's a really good guy. We
OL,20,Fused to get the school bus every day
OL,21,Ftogether.
