OL,3,C'Kind and talented': Tributes paid to
OL,4,CLiam Payne after his death
OL,6,F"My memories of him are of that bowl-
OL,7,Fcutted teenager who was on the X
OL,8,FFactor and the last time I saw him he
OL,9,Fwas about to go on the X Factor the
OL,10,Fsecond time.
OL,12,F"I basically said 'good luck mate, I
OL,13,Freally wish you the best, I hope it
OL,14,Fworks out for you' and off he went and
OL,15,Fthen literally a year later we were
OL,16,Fdancing around to his 'What Makes you
OL,17,FBeautiful' by One Direction and I was
OL,18,Flike 'I know this guy'!"
