OL,6,F"(It is) really sad and tragic news
OL,7,Fand to me that's how I'll remember
OL,8,FLiam - as being that lovely lad from
OL,9,FWolverhampton who's from where I'm
OL,10,Ffrom originally."
OL,12,FThe pop star's school, St Peter's
OL,13,FCollegiate Academy in Wolverhampton,
OL,14,Fwrote in a statement it was "deeply
OL,15,Fsaddened" to learn of their former
OL,16,Fstudent's death.
