OL,3,C'Kind and talented': Tributes paid to
OL,4,CLiam Payne after his death
OL,6,FIt said: "During his time at St
OL,7,FPeter's Collegiate Academy, Liam was
OL,8,Fnot only well-liked by his peers and
OL,9,Fteachers but also recognised for his
OL,10,Ftalents."
OL,12,F"He made a positive impact on our
OL,13,Fschool community, and his
OL,14,Fcontributions will be remembered.
OL,16,F"Our thoughts are with Liam's family
OL,17,Fand friends during this difficult
OL,18,Ftime. We extend our sincere
OL,19,Fcondolences to all those affected by
OL,20,Fhis passing."
