OL,6,FWest Bromwich Albion paid tribute to
OL,7,Ftheir fan on X writing: "We're shocked
OL,8,Fand saddened to learn of the passing
OL,9,Fof Baggies fan and musician, Liam
OL,10,FPayne.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts are with Liam's family,
OL,13,Ffriends and loved ones at this tragic
OL,14,Ftime."
OL,16,FIn a statement City of Wolverhampton
OL,17,FCollege said: "We were sorry to hear
OL,18,Fthe news about former student Liam
OL,19,FPayne and wish to extend our
OL,20,Fsympathies to his family and friends
OL,21,Fat this very sad time."
