OL,3,C'Kind and talented': Tributes paid to
OL,4,CLiam Payne after his death
OL,6,F"He has been taken from the world so
OL,7,Fyoung"
OL,9,FThe Mayor of Wolverhampton said: "The
OL,10,FCity of Wolverhampton is extremely
OL,11,Fproud of Liam, a young man from humble
OL,12,Fbeginnings who went on to achieve
OL,13,Fglobal stardom with millions of fans
OL,14,Faround the world.
OL,16,F"I know that members of his family
OL,17,Fstill live locally and I wish to send
OL,18,Fmy sincere condolences to them for the
OL,19,Funimaginable grief they must be
OL,20,Fexperiencing.
