OL,3,C'Kind and talented': Tributes paid to
OL,4,CLiam Payne after his death
OL,6,F"It is tragic to think he has been
OL,7,Ftaken from the world so young, it
OL,8,Fdoesn't seem long ago that he was
OL,9,Fperforming with the rest of One
OL,10,FDirection in Wolverhampton city centre
OL,11,Fduring those X Factor days when their
OL,12,Ffame was just beginning.
OL,14,F"Our thoughts today are with all those
OL,15,Fwho knew and loved Liam, may he rest
OL,16,Fin peace."
OL,18,FThe University of Wolverhampton, which
OL,19,Fnamed Payne as one of the city's
OL,20,F'Famous Sons & Daughters' joined those
OL,21,Fpaying tribute to him.
