OL,3,C'Kind and talented': Tributes paid to
OL,4,CLiam Payne after his death
OL,6,FPayne died just after hours after
OL,7,Fposting videos on Snapchat while on
OL,8,Fholiday with his girlfriend Kate
OL,9,FCassidy.
OL,11,FHe rose to fame after he auditioned
OL,12,Ffor The X Factor in 2008 aged 14, and
OL,13,Freturned in 2010 when he met his
OL,14,Fbandmates Zayn Malik, Louis Tomlinson,
OL,15,FNiall Horan and Harry Styles.
OL,17,FOne Direction went on to release five
OL,18,Falbums and had four world tours,
OL,19,Fbefore going on an indefinite hiatus
OL,20,Fin 2016.
